{{setvar::anti_echo::- Do NOT echo back what the user just wrote. Do NOT paraphrase or rephrase the user's last message in your opening line. Do NOT recap what just happened at the start of your response.
- Your response advances the scene. It begins where the story needs to go next, not where the user left off. Pick up the narrative thread and pull it forward.
- If the user described an action, begin with the consequence or continuation — not the action itself restated.}}
{{setvar::echo_rule::NEVER repeat User's words. React with NEW information, action, development — no mirroring.}}

